			CSS Margin - Individual Sides

	CSS has properties for specifying the margin for each side of an element: 

	margin-top

	margin-right

	margin-bottom

	margin-left

	All the margin properties can have the following values: 

	auto - the browser calculates the margin

	length - specifies a margin in px, pt, cm, etc.

	inherit - specifies that the margin should be inherited from the parent element

	Tip: Negative values are allowed. 

	The following example sets different margins for all four sides of a <p> element: 

	 Example

	 p {
  	 margin-top: 100px;
 	 margin-bottom: 100px;
 	 margin-right: 150px;
 	 margin-left: 80px;
	 }



Margin - Shorthand Property

To shorten the code, it is possible to specify all the margin properties in one property.

The margin property is a shorthand property for the following individual margin properties: 

	 margin-top

	 margin-right

	 margin-bottom

	 margin-left

	 So, here is how it works: 

	 If the margin property has four values: 

	 margin: 25px 50px 75px 100px; 

	 top margin is 25px

	 right margin is 50px

	 bottom margin is 75px

	 left margin is 100px


	 Example

	 p {

 	 margin: 25px 50px 75px 100px; 

	 } 

	 If the margin property has three values: 

	 margin: 25px 50px 75px; 

	 top margin is 25px

	 right and left margins are 50px

	 bottom margin is 75px


	 Example

	 p {

 	 margin: 25px 50px 75px; 

	 } 

	 If the margin property has two values: 

	 margin: 25px 50px; 

	 top and bottom margins are 25px

	 right and left margins are 50px


	 Example

	 p {

 	 margin: 25px 50px; 

	 } 

	 If the margin property has one value: 

	 margin: 25px; 

	 all four margins are 25px


	 Example

	 p {

 	 margin: 25px; 

	 } 



 CSS Padding - Individual Sides

	 CSS has properties for specifying the padding for each side of an element: 

	 padding-top

	 padding-right

	 padding-bottom

	 padding-left

	 All the padding properties can have the following values: 

	 length - specifies a padding in px, pt, cm, etc. 

	 inherit - specifies that the padding should be inherited from the parent element

	 Note: Negative values are not allowed. 

	 The following example sets different padding for all four sides of a <div> element:


	 Example

	 div {

 	 padding-top: 50px; 

 	 padding-right: 30px; 

 	 padding-bottom: 50px; 

  	 padding-left: 80px; 

	 } 



Padding - Shorthand Property

	 To shorten the code, it is possible to specify all the padding properties in one property.

	 The padding property is a shorthand property for the following individual padding

 	 properties: 

	 padding-top

	 padding-right

	 padding-bottom

	 padding-left

	 So, here is how it works: 

	 If the padding property has four values: 

	 padding: 25px 50px 75px 100px; 

	 top padding is 25px

	 right padding is 50px

	 bottom padding is 75px

	 left padding is 100px

	 Example


	 div {

	  padding: 25px 50px 75px 100px; 

	 } 

	 If the padding property has three values: 

	 padding: 25px 50px 75px; 

	 top padding is 25px

	 right and left paddings are 50px

	 bottom padding is 75px


	 Example

	 div {

	  padding: 25px 50px 75px; 

	 }


	 If the padding property has two values: 

	 padding: 25px 50px; 

	 top and bottom paddings are 25px

	 right and left paddings are 50px 

	 If the padding property has one value: 

	 padding: 25px; 

	 all four padding are 25px


	 Example

	 p {

 	 padding: 25px; 

	}

			CSS Text


Text Color
 	 The color property is used to set the color of the text. The color is specified by: 
 	 a color name - like "red"
 	 The default text color for a page is defined in the body selector. 

 	 Example
 	 body {
 	 color: blue; 
 	 }

	 h1 {
 	 color: green; 
 	 } 

 Text Alignment
 	 The text-align property is used to set the horizontal alignment of a text. 
 	 A text can be left or right aligned, centered, or justified. 
 	 The following example shows center aligned, and left and right aligned text (left alignment is default if text direction is left-to-right, and right alignment is default if text direction is right-to-left): 

 Example
 	 h1 {
 	 text-align: center; 
 	 }

	 h2 {
 	 text-align: left; 
 	 }


Text Decoration
 	 The text-decoration property is used to set or remove decorations from text. 
 	 The value text-decoration: none; is often used to remove underlines from links: 

 Example
 	 a {
 	 text-decoration: none; 
 	 } 
 	 The other text-decoration values are used to decorate text: 

 Example
 	 h1 {
 	 text-decoration: overline; 
 	 }

	 h2 {
 	 text-decoration: line-through; 
 	 }


Text Transformation
 	 The text-transform property is used to specify uppercase and lowercase letters in a text. 
 	 It can be used to turn everything into uppercase or lowercase letters, or capitalize the 
 	 first letter of each word: 

 Example
 	 p.uppercase {
 	 text-transform: uppercase; 
 	 }

	 p.lowercase {
 	 text-transform: lowercase; 
 	 }


CSS Fonts
 	 Font Family
 	 The font family of a text is set with the font-family property. 
 	 The font-family property should hold several font names as a /"fallback"/ system. If the 
 	 browser does not support the first font, it tries the next font, and so on. 
 	 Start with the font you want, and end with a generic family, to let the browser pick a
 	 similar font in the generic family, if no other fonts are available. 
 	 Note: If the name of a font family is more than one word, it must be in quotation marks, 
 	 like: "Times New Roman".
 	 More than one font family is specified in a comma-separated list: 

 Example
 	 p {
 	 font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif; 
 	 } 


Font Style
 	 The font-style property is mostly used to specify italic text. 
 	 This property has three values: 
 	 normal - The text is shown normally
 	 italic - The text is shown in italics
 	 oblique - The text is "leaning" (oblique is very similar to italic, but less 
 supported) 

 	 Example
 	 p.normal {
 font-style: normal; 
 	 }

	 p.italic {
 font-style: italic; 
 	 }

	 p.oblique {
 font-style: oblique; 
 	 } 


Font Size With Pixels
 	 Setting the text size with pixels gives you full control over the text size: 

 Example
 	 h1 {
 	 font-size: 40px; 
 	 }

	 h2 {
 	 font-size: 30px; 
 	 }


Font Weight
 	 The font-weight property specifies the weight of a font: 

 Example
 	 p.normal {
 	 font-weight: normal; 
 	 }

	 p.thick {
 	 font-weight: bold; 
 	}

                       			BANGO CSS


       Ana amfani da abubuwan da suka gabata na CSS don ayyana tasirin bango don abubuwan. 

       	 Bayanan al'ummomin CSS: 

       • 	 baya-launi 

       • 	-hoton 

       • 	 baya-maimaita 

       • 	 tushen abin da aka makala 

       • 	 tushen-baya 



       	 Bango mai launi 

        	 Dukiya mai launi mai launi tana fayyace launi na asalin al'adar. 

        	 An sanya asalin shafin kamar haka: 


        	 Misalin \ n
         	 body { 

        	 background-color: lightblue; 

        	 }



       	 CSS, wani launi yakan fi dacewa da: 

       • 	 sunan launi mai inganci - kamar "ja" 

       • 	 wani darajar HEX - kamar "# ff0000" 

       • 	 an darajar RGB - kamar "rgb (255,0,0)" 

       	 A cikin misalin da ke ƙasa, abubuwan <h1>, <p>, da <div> suna da banbanci masana: 

       	 Misalin 

       	 h1 {

       	  background-color: green;

       	 }


       	 div {

        	 background-color: lightblue;

       	 }


       	 p {

       	  background-color: yellow;

       	 }



       	 Hotunan Bango 

       	 Ginin-bayan hoton yana nuna hoto don amfani da shi azaman asalin samfurin. 

       	 Ta hanyar tsoho, ana maimaita hoton don haka ya rufe duka abubuwan. 

       	 Hoto na baya na shafin za'a iya saita shi kamar haka: 


       	 Misalin \ n
       	 body { 

        	 background-image: url("paper.gif"); 

       	 } 



       	 Da ke ƙasa akwai misalin mummunan haɗuwa da rubutu da hoton baya. Rubutun ba wuya ake karanta shi ba: 


       	 Misalin 

       	 body {

        	 background-image: url("bgdesert.jpg");

       	 } 



       	 Lura: Lokacin amfani da hoton bango, yi amfani da hoto wanda baya rikitar da rubutu. 



       	 Hotunan Bayan Fage - Maimaita kai tsaye ko a kai tsaye

       	Ta hanyar tsohuwar, dukiya ta bayan-hoto tana maimaita hoto ta fuska biyu kuma a tsaye.

       	 Wasu hotunan yakamata a maimaita su kawai a kwance ko a tsaye, ko kuma za su yi kama da juna, kamar haka:


       	 Misali 

       	 body {
        	 background-image: url("gradient_bg.png");

       	 }



       	 Idan hoton da ke sama ana maimaita shi kawai a sama (bayan-maimaita: maimaita-x;), bango zai yi kyau: 


       	 Misalin 

       	 body {

        	 background-image: url("gradient_bg.png"); 

        	 background-repeat: repeat-x; 

       	 } 



       	 Tukwici: Don maimaita hoto tsaye, saita bango-maimaita: maimaita-y; 



       Hoton Farko - Sanya matsayi kuma ba-sake 

       	 Nuna hoton bango kawai sau daya kuma ana tantance shi ta hanyar asalin-maimaita dukiya: 


       Misali 

       	 body {

       	  background-image: url("img_tree.png"); 

       	  background-repeat: no-repeat; 

       	 } 



       	 Matsayin hoton an tantance shi ta hanyar tushen matsayin: 



       	 Misalin 

       	 body {

        	 background-image: url("img_tree.png"); 

        	 background-repeat: no-repeat; 

        	 background-position: right top; 

       	  } 



       Hoton Fage - Matsayin da aka kafa 

       	 Don tantance cewa yakamata a daidaita hoton asalin (bazai jujjuya tare da sauran n ba shafin), yi amfani da kayan haɗin-baya: 


       	 Misalin \ n
       	 body {

       	  background-image: url("img_tree.png");  

       	  background-repeat: no-repeat; 

       	  background-position: right top; 

       	  background-attachment: fixed; 

       	 } 



       Nisaren kan iyaka 

       	 propertyasar da ke kan iyaka tana ƙaddara girman kan iyakoki huɗu. 

       	 Za'a iya saita nisa azaman takamaiman girman (a px, pt, cm, em, da sauransu) ko ta amfani da ɗayan 
	 uku da aka ƙaddara: bakin ciki, matsakaici, ko kauri. 

       	 -asar da ke kan iyaka za ta iya kasancewa daga dabi'u ɗaya zuwa huɗu (don kan iyaka, dama iyaka, iyaka, da iyaka ta hagu). 


       	 Misalin 

       	 p.one { 

       	  border-style: solid; 

       	  border-width: 5px; 

       }


       	 p.two { 

        	 border-style: solid; 

       	  border-width: medium; 

       }


       	 p.three {

       	  border-style: solid; 

        	 border-width: 2px 10px 4px 20px; 

       	 } 



       Launi mai iyaka 

       	 Ana amfani da kadara mai launi-launi don saita launi na kan iyakoki huɗu. 

       	 Za'a iya saita launi ta: 

       • 	 suna - saka sunan launi, kamar "ja" 

       • 	 Hex - saka ƙimar hex, kamar "#ff0000" 

       • 	 RGB - saka darajar RGB, kamar "rgb (255,0,0)" 

       • 	 Bayyanawa 


       	 -asar mai launi-launi na iya samun daga dabi'u ɗaya zuwa huɗu (don kan iyaka, dama, iyakar, iyaka, da iyakar hagu). 

       	 Idan ba'a saita launi-iyaka ba, zai gaji daɗin adon. 

       	 Iyakokin Red 


       	 Misalin 

       	 p.one { 

        	 border-style: solid; 

        	 border-color: red; 

       	 }


       	 p.two { 

       	  border-style: solid; 

        	 border-color: green; 

       	 } 


       	 p.three { 

       	  border-style: solid; 

       	  border-color: red green blue yellow; 

       	 }



       Kan iyaka - daidaikun mutane 

       	 Daga misalan da ke sama kun ga cewa yana yiwuwa a tantance sabanin 

       	 iyaka ga kowane gefe. 

       	 A CSS, akwai kuma kaddarorin don tantance kowane kan iyakokin (saman, dama, 

       	 kasa, da hagu): 

       	 Tsarin Bango daban-daban 


       	 Misalin \ n
       	 p { 

       	  border-top-style: dotted; 

        	 border-right-style: solid; 

        	 border-bottom-style: dotted; 

        	 border-left-style: solid; 

       	 } 



       \ t Misalin da ke sama yana bada sakamako iri ɗaya kamar haka: 


       \ t Misalin \ n
       	 p { 

        	 border-style: dotted solid; 

       	 } 



       	 Don haka, ga yadda yake aiki: 

       	 Idan dukiyar da ke kan iyaka tana da dabi'u huɗa: 

       • 	 iyaka-style: dotted solid dashed; 

       \sashin saman iyaka yana da alama

       	 iyakar iyaka tana da ƙarfi 

       	 kasan iyakar ta ninka biyu 



        \yankin iyakar hagu ya rushe 

       	 Idan dukiyar da ke kan iyakar tana da dabi'u uku: 

       • 	 iyaka-style: dotted m ninki biyu; 

       	 sashin saman iyaka yana da alama 

        	 dama da iyakokin hagu suna da ƙarfi 

        	 kasan iyakar ta ninka biyu 

       	 Idan dukiyar da ke kan iyaka tana da dabi'u biyu: 

       • 	 iyaka-style: dotted solid; 

        	 saman layi da na ƙasa dotted 

        	 dama da iyakokin hagu suna da ƙarfi 

       	 Idan dukiyar da ke kan iyakokin tana da darajar guda ɗaya: 

       • saitin kan iyaka: dotted; 

         	duk shingayen hudun suna da ma'ana 

       	 Ana amfani da kadarar da ke kan iyaka a misalin da ke sama. Koyaya, yana kuma aiki tare da 

       	 iyakar iyaka da launi-launi.

			Rubutun CSS 

 Launin Rubutu 
 	 Ana amfani da kayan launi don saita launi na rubutu. An bayyana launi ta: 
 • 	 sunan launi - kamar "ja" 
 	 Tsarin rubutu na tsohuwa don shafi an bayyana shi cikin zaɓin jiki. 
 	 Misalin 
 	 jiki {
 	 launi: shuɗi; 
 	} 

	 h1 {
 	 launi: kore; 
 	} 


Rubutun rubutu 
 	 Ana amfani da kayan-daidaita rubutu don saita kwance a rubutu na rubutu. 
 	 Rubutun zai iya barin hagu ko dama, daidaita, ko daidaituwa. 
 	 Misali masu zuwa suna nuna tsararren rubutu a tsakiya, da hagu da dama na rubutu masu rubutu (hagu 
 	 karkatarwa tsoho ne idan allon rubutu ya kasance hagu-dama, kuma jeri na dama tsoho ne idan rubutu 

 Misali 
 shugabanci hannun dama ne zuwa hagu):
 	 h1 {
 	 text-align: center; 
 	 }

	 h2 {
 	 text-align: left; 
 	 }


Rubutun Kaya 
 	 Ana amfani da kayan adon rubutu don saitawa ko cire kayan ado daga rubutu. 
 	 Darajar rubutu-ƙyalli: babu; galibi ana amfani da shi don cire layin tattaunawa daga hanyoyin: 

 Misali 

	 a {
 	 text-decoration: none; 
 	 } 


	 Sauran hanyoyin rubutu na adon rubutu ana amfani dasu don yin ado da rubutu: 


Misali 

	 h1 {
 	 text-decoration: overline; 
 	 }

	 h2 {
 	 text-decoration: line-through; 
 	 }


Canjin rubutu 
 	 Ana amfani da abin da za a yi amfani da kayan rubutu wajen tantance manyan haruffa da ƙananan inan rubutu a cikin rubutu. 
 	 Ana iya amfani da shi don juya komai zuwa babba ko ƙananan baƙaƙe, ko cinye 
 	 harafin farko na kowace kalma: 


Misali 

	 p.uppercase {
 	 text-transform: uppercase; 
 	 }

	 p.lowercase {
 	 text-transform: lowercase; 
 	 }


CSS Fonts 
 	 Gidan dangi 
 	 Gidan font na rubutu an saita shi tare da kayan iyali-font. 
 	 Dukiyar dan-dan-font ya kamata ya riƙe sunaye da yawa na font a matsayin "faɗuwa" tsarin. Idan 
 	 mai bincike baya goyan bayan font na farko, yana ƙoƙari font na gaba, da sauransu. 
 	 Fara daga font da kake so, kuma ƙare tare da dangi na kowa, don barin mai binciken ya zaɓi 
 Kundin font iri daya a cikin dangi, idan babu sauran rubutun. 
 	 Bayani: Idan sunan ɗan font ya fi kalma ɗaya, dole ne ya kasance cikin alamun faɗar, 

 son kamar: "Times New Roman". 
 	 Fiye da gidan font an tantance a cikin jerin wakafi-rabu: 


Misali 

	 p {
 	 font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif; 
 	 } 


Salon Harafi 
 	 Ana amfani da dukiyar da ake amfani da rubutu don nuna rubutu ko rubutun rubutu. 
 	 Wannan dukiya tana da dabi'u uku: 
 • 	 al'ada - Ana nuna rubutun a al'ada 
 • 	 Italic - Rubutun yana nuna a cikin rubutun. 
 • 	 oblique - Rubutun yana "jingina" (duk da haka oblique yana da kama da ta hanyar rubutun ta, amma ƙasa da n \ goyan baya) 

 	 Misalin 
 	 p.normal {
 font-style: normal; 
 	 }

	 p.italic {
 font-style: italic; 
 	 }

	 p.oblique {
 font-style: oblique; 
 	 } 


Girman Font Tare da Pixels 
 	 Saitin rubutun rubutu da pixels yana baka cikakken iko akan girman rubutun: 

 Misali 
 	 h1 {
 	 font-size: 40px; 
 	 }

	 h2 {
 	 font-size: 30px; 
 	 }


Nauyi Font 
 	 Dukiyar-font-nauyi ta bayyana nauyin font: 

 Misali 
 	 p.normal {
 	 font-weight: normal; 
 	 }

	 p.thick {
 	 font-weight: bold; 
 	}

 			Ifihan CSS


Kini CSS?

•	 CSS duro fun Awọn awoṣe ara Cascading

•	 CSS ṣapejuwe bi o ṣe le ṣe afihan awọn eroja HTML loju iboju, iwe, tabi ni awọn media miiran

•	 CSS ṣe ipamọ iṣẹ pupọ. O le ṣakoso ifilelẹ ti awọn oju opo wẹẹbu ọpọ ni ẹẹkan

•	 Awọn aṣọ ita ti wa ni fipamọ ni awọn faili CSS


Kini idi ti o lo CSS?

A lo CSS lati ṣalaye awọn aza fun awọn oju opo wẹẹbu rẹ, pẹlu apẹrẹ, akọkọ ati awọn iyatọ ninu ifihan fun awọn ẹrọ oriṣiriṣi ati titobi iboju.



CSS yanju Iṣoro Nla kan

HTML ko MII pinnu lati ni awọn aami fun ọna kika oju-iwe wẹẹbu kan!

A ṣẹda HTML lati ṣe apejuwe akoonu ti oju-iwe wẹẹbu kan, bii:

<H1> Eyi ni akọle </H1>

<p> Eyi ni ìpínrọ kan. </p>

Nigbati awọn afi bii <font>, ati awọn eroja ti awọ ni a ṣafikun si HTML 3.2 sipesifikesonu, o bẹrẹ alaburuku fun awọn olulo wẹẹbu. Idagbasoke ti awọn oju opo wẹẹbu nla, nibiti a ti fi awọn akọwe ati alaye awọ si gbogbo oju-iwe kan ṣoṣo, di ilana gigun ati gbowolori.

Lati yanju iṣoro yii, Consortium World Wide Web (W3C) ṣẹda CSS.

CSS kuro ni ọna kika ọna lati oju-iwe HTML!

CSS Ṣàfipamọ Loti ti Iṣẹ!

Awọn asọ-ara ti wa ni fipamọ deede ni awọn faili .css ita.

Pẹlu faili itankale itagbangba, o le yi iwo oju opo wẹẹbu pada nipa yiyipada faili kan!





CSS Syntax ati Selectors


Syntax CSS

Ofin CSS kan ti o jẹ ti yiyan ati bulọ ikede:




Awọn olutayan tọka si nkan HTML ti o fẹ lati ara.

Àkọsílẹ ìpolongo ni ọkan tabi diẹ awọn ikede ti o ya sọtọ nipasẹ semicolons.

Ifiwe kọọkan pẹlu orukọ ohun-ini CSS ati iye kan, ti o ya sọtọ nipasẹ oluṣafihan.

Ifiweranṣẹ CSS kan pari pẹlu semikilonni kan, ati pe awọn bulọọki ikede ni o wa yika nipasẹ awọn àmúró iṣupọ.

Ninu apẹẹrẹ atẹle gbogbo awọn eroja <p> yoo jẹ abulẹ ni aarin, pẹlu awọ ọrọ pupa:



Apẹẹrẹ

p {

  awọ: pupa;

  ọrọ-align: aarin;

}



awọn olutapa CSS

awọn olutapa CSS ni a lo lati \“wa\” (tabi yan) awọn eroja HTML ti o da lori orukọ eroja wọn, id, kilasi, isọda, ati diẹ sii.




Awọn ano Selector

Ẹya aṣeduro yan awọn eroja ti o da lori orukọ ano.

O le yan gbogbo awọn eroja <p> lori oju-iwe bi eleyi (ni idi eyi, gbogbo awọn eroja </p> yoo jẹ isọdi aarin, pẹlu awọ ọrọ pupa kan):



Apẹẹrẹ

p {

  ọrọ-align: aarin;

  awọ: pupa;

}



Awọn id Selector

Oluṣakoso id naa nlo abuda id ti ẹya HTML lati yan ipin kan pato.

Awọn id ti ano yẹ ki o jẹ alailẹgbẹ laarin oju-iwe kan, nitorinaa a ti lo id yiyan ti a yan lati yan ọkan alailẹgbẹ kan!

Lati yan ipin kan pẹlu id kan pato, kọ kikọ silẹ (#) kan, atẹle nipa id ti ano.

Ofin aṣa ti o wa ni isalẹ yoo lo si nkan HTML pẹlu id = "para1":


Apẹẹrẹ

# para1 {

  ọrọ-align: aarin;

  awọ: pupa;

}


Awọn kilasi Selector

Olumulo kilasi yan awọn eroja pẹlu abuda kilasi pàtó kan.

Lati yan awọn eroja pẹlu kilasi kan pato, kọ akoko kan (.) Kikọ, atẹle nipa orukọ ti kilasi naa.

Ninu apẹẹrẹ ni isalẹ, gbogbo awọn eroja HTML pẹlu kilasi = "ile-iṣẹ" yoo jẹ pupa ati ila-aarin



Apẹẹrẹ

.aarin {

  ọrọ-align: aarin;

  awọ: pupa;

}



O tun le ṣalaye pe awọn eroja HTML pato kan yẹ ki o ni ipa nipasẹ kilasi kan.

Ninu apẹẹrẹ ni isalẹ, awọn eroja <p> nikan pẹlu kilasi = "aarin" yoo wa ni isọdọkan aarin:


Apẹẹrẹ

p.center {

  ọrọ-align: aarin;

  awọ: pupa;

}



Awọn eroja HTML tun le tọka si siwaju ju kilasi kan lọ.

Ninu apẹẹrẹ ni isalẹ, ipilẹ </p> yoo jẹ ara ni ibamu si kilasi = "aarin" ati si kilasi = "nla":


Apẹẹrẹ

<p kilasi = "ile-iṣẹ ti o tobi"> Apaadi yii tọka si awọn kilasi meji. </p>



Akiyesi: Orukọ kilasi ko le bẹrẹ pẹlu nọmba kan!




Awọn yiyan Ẹgbẹ

Ti o ba ni awọn eroja pẹlu asọye ara kanna, bi eleyi:

h1 {

  ọrọ-align: aarin;

  awọ: pupa;

}


h2 {

  ọrọ-align: aarin;

  awọ: pupa;

}


p {

  ọrọ-align: aarin;

  awọ: pupa;

}



Yoo dara julọ lati ṣajọpọ awọn ti o yan, lati dinku koodu naa.

Si awọn olukọ ẹgbẹ, ya onyan yiyan pẹlu komma kan.

Ninu apẹẹrẹ ti o wa ni isalẹ a ti ṣe akojọ awọn yiyan lati koodu ti o wa loke:


Apẹẹrẹ

h1, h2, p {

  ọrọ-align: aarin;

  awọ: pupa;

}:

			Ala CSS - Olumulo Kọọkan Sirin 

	 CSS ni awọn ohun-ini fun sisọ ala fun ẹgbẹ kọọkan ti ano: 

	margin-top

	margin-right

	margin-bottom

	margin-left



	 Gbogbo awọn ohun-ini ala le ni awọn iye wọnyi: 

	auto - the browser calculates the margin

	length - specifies a margin in px, pt, cm, etc.

	inherit - specifies that the margin should be inherited from the parent element



	 Tip: Awọn iye odi jẹ gba laaye. 

\ t Apẹẹrẹ atẹle n ṣeto awọn ala oriṣiriṣi si gbogbo awọn ẹgbẹ mẹrin ti ipilẹ <p> kan: 


\ t Apeere \ n
	 p {

  	 margin-top: 100px;

 	 margin-bottom: 100px;

 	 margin-right: 150px;

 	 margin-left: 80px;

	 } 



Ala - Ohun-ini Shorthand 

Lati kuru koodu, o ṣee ṣe lati tokasi gbogbo awọn ohun-ala ni ohun-ini kan.

Ohun-ini ala jẹ ohun-ini kukuru fun atẹle awọn ohun-ini ala-kọọkan ti n tẹle: 

	 margin-top

	 margin-right

	 margin-bottom

	 margin-left


	 Nitorinaa, eyi ni bi o ṣe n ṣiṣẹ: 

	 Ti ohun-ini ala 
 ba ni awọn iye mẹrin: 

 	 ala: 25px 50px 75px 100px; 

	 oke ni 25px 

 	 ala ọtun jẹ 50px

	 ala isalẹ jẹ 75px 

 	 osi ipin jẹ 100px 


	 Apeere 

	 p {

 	 margin: 25px 50px 75px 100px; 

	 } 



	 Ti ohun-ini ala ba ni awọn iye mẹta: 

• 	 ala: 25px 50px 75px; 

 	 oke ni 25px 

 	 ọtun ati apa osi jẹ 50px 

	 ala isalẹ jẹ 75px 

	 Apeere 

	 p {

 	 margin: 25px 50px 75px; 

	 } 



	 Ti ohun-ini ala ni awọn iye meji: 

• 	 ala: 25px 50px; 

 	 oke ati isalẹ awọn ala jẹ 25px 

	 ọtun ati apa osi jẹ 50px 

	 Apeere 

	 p {

 	 margin: 25px 50px; 

	 } 



	 Ti ohun-ini ala ba ni iye kan: 


• 	 ala: 25px; 

	 gbogbo awọn igun mẹrin ni 25px 


	 Apeere 

	 p {

 	 margin: 25px; 

	 } 



Ohun elo CSS - Awọn igbidanwo Kọọkan 

	 CSS ni awọn ohun-ini fun sisọ padi fun ẹgbẹ kọọkan ti ano: 

	 padding-top

	 padding-right

	 padding-bottom

	 padding-left



	 Gbogbo awọn ohun-elo fifọ le ni awọn iye wọnyi: 

	 length - specifies a padding in px, pt, cm, etc. 

	 inherit - specifies that the padding should be inherited from the parent element



	 Akiyesi: A ko gba laaye awọn odi . 

	 Apẹẹrẹ to tẹle ṣeto padding oriṣiriṣi fun gbogbo awọn ẹgbẹ mẹrin ti ipilẹ <div>: 


	 Apeere 

	 div {

 	 padding-top: 50px; 

 	 padding-right: 30px; 

 	 padding-bottom: 50px; 

  	 padding-left: 80px; 

	 } 



Sisọ - Ohun-ini kukuru. 

	 Lati ṣoki koodu, o ṣee ṣe lati tokasi gbogbo awọn ohun-elo fifọ ni ohun-ini kan. 

	 Ohun-elo fifọ jẹ ohun-ini kukuru fun ohun elo mimu kọọkan ti n tẹle 


 	 Awọn ohun-ini: 

	 Nitorinaa, eyi ni bi o ṣe n ṣiṣẹ: 

	 Ti ohun-elo fifọ naa ni awọn idiyele mẹrin: 

• 	 padding: 25px 50px 75px 100px; 

	 padding oke ni 25px 

	 padding ọtun jẹ 50px 

	 isalẹ fifẹ jẹ 75px 

	 padding osi jẹ 100px 


	 Apeere 

	 div {

	 ẹmu: 25px 50px 75px 100px; 



	 Ti ohun-elo fifọ naa ni awọn idiyele mẹta: 

• 	 padding: 25px 50px 75px; 

	 padding oke ni 25px 

	 sọtun ati sosi apoti wa ni 50px 

	 isalẹ fifẹ jẹ 75px 


	 Apeere 

	 div {

	 ẹmu: 25px 50px 75px; 

	}



	 Ti ohun-elo fifọ ni awọn iye meji: 

• 	 padding: 25px 50px; 

	 oke ati isalẹ awọn paddings jẹ 25px 

	 sọtun ati sosi apoti wa ni 50px 

	 Ti ohun-elo fifọ naa ni iye kan: 

• 	 padding: 25px; 

	 gbogbo awọn fifẹ mẹrin jẹ 25px 

	 Apeere 

	 p {

 	 padding: 25px; 

	}

			Text CSS

 Awọ ọrọ 
 	 A lo ohun-ini awọ lati ṣeto awọ ti ọrọ. A sọ asọtẹlẹ naa nipasẹ: 
 • 	 orukọ awọ kan - bi "pupa" 
 	 Ayipada ọrọ awọ fun oju-iwe kan ni asọye ninu yiyan ara. 

 	 Apeere 
 	 body {
 	 color: blue; 
 	 }

	 h1 {
 	 color: green; 
 	 } 


Ifọwọsi Text 
 	 Ohun-elo aligning ọrọ naa ti lo lati ṣeto tito petele ti ọrọ kan. 
 	 A le fi ọrọ silẹ tabi apa otun, ti dojukọ, tabi lare. 
 	 Apẹẹrẹ atẹle n ṣe afihan titọ aarin, ati osi ati apa ọtun ọrọ ti a ge ni ọwọ (osi 
 & t ọrọ 
 itọsọna jẹ ọtun-si-osi): 

 Apeere 
 	 h1 {
 	 text-align: center; 
 	 }

	 h2 {
 	 text-align: left; 
 	 }


Ohun ọṣọ Text 
 	 Ohun-ọṣọ ọrọ ti lo lati ṣeto tabi yọ awọn ohun-ọṣọ kuro ninu ọrọ. 
 	 Ohun ọṣọ ọrọ-ọṣọ: ko si; ni a maa n lo nigbagbogbo lati yọ awọn atokọ kuro lati awọn ọna asopọ: 

 Apeere 
 	 a {
 	 text-decoration: none; 
 	 } 


Awọn iye-ọṣọ ọrọ miiran ni a lo lati ṣe ọṣọ ọrọ: 

 	 Apeere 
 	 h1 {
 	 text-decoration: overline; 
 	 }

	 h2 {
 	 text-decoration: line-through; 
 	 }


Iyipada Ọrọ 
 	 Ohun-ini ọrọ-yipada ti lo lati ṣe afihan awọn lẹta nla ati kekere ni ọrọ kan. 
 	 O le ṣee lo lati tan ohun gbogbo sinu apoti kekere tabi awọn lẹta kekere, tabi kawewe awọn 
 	 lẹta akọkọ ti ọrọ kọọkan: 

 Apeere 

	 p.uppercase {
 	 text-transform: uppercase; 
 	 }

	 p.lowercase {
 	 text-transform: lowercase; 
 	 }


Awọn fọnti CSS 

	 Font idile 
 	 Awọn idile fonti ti ọrọ ti ṣeto pẹlu ohun-ini idile. 
 	 Ohun-ini fonti-idile yẹ ki o mu ọpọlọpọ awọn orukọ font han bi eto \“isubu\” eto. Ti o ba ti 
 	 aṣawakiri ko ṣe atilẹyin fonti akọkọ, o n gbiyanju fonti atẹle, ati bẹbẹ lọ. 
 	 Bẹrẹ pẹlu akọ-ọrọ ti o fẹ, ati pari pẹlu idile jeneriki, lati jẹ ki aṣawakiri mu ohun 
 	 font ti o jọra ninu idile jeneriki, ti ko ba awọn akọwe miiran wa. 
 	 Akiyesi: Ti orukọ idile ẹbi ba ju ọrọ kan lọ, o gbọdọ wa ni awọn ami ọrọ asọye, 
 	 fẹran: "Times New Roman". 
 	 Diẹ ẹ sii ju idile font kan ni pato ninu atokọ ti o pin ipin-sọtọ: 

 Apeere 
 	 p {
 	 font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif; 
 	 } 


Font Style 
 	 Ohun-ini font-ara ni a lo igbagbogbo lati ṣe apejuwe ọrọ italiki. 
 	 Ohun-ini yii ni awọn idiyele mẹta: 
 	 normal - The text is shown normally
 	 italic - The text is shown in italics
 	 oblique - The text is "leaning" (oblique is very similar to italic, but less 
 supported) 


	 Apeere 
 	 p.normal {
 font-style: normal; 
 	 }

	 p.italic {
 font-style: italic; 
 	 }

	 p.oblique {
 font-style: oblique; 
 	 } 


Iwọn Font Pẹlu Awọn piksẹli 
 	 Ṣiṣeto iwọn ọrọ pẹlu awọn piksẹli yoo fun ọ ni iṣakoso ni kikun lori iwọn ọrọ: 

 Apeere 
 	 h1 {
 	 font-size: 40px; 
 	 }

	 h2 {
 	 font-size: 30px; 
 	 }


Iwuwo Font 
 	 Ohun-ini fonti-n ṣalaye iwuwo ti fonti: 

 Apeere 
 	 p.normal {
 	 font-weight: normal; 
 	 }

	 p.thick {
 	 font-weight: bold; 
 	}

       			Okwu Ntinye CSS 


       	 Gịnị bụ CSS? 

       • 	 CSS guzo maka Cascading Style Sheets 

       • 	 CSS kowara etu aga - esi gosiputa ihe HTML na enyo, akwukwo, ma obu n\’ime mgbasa ozi ndi ozo

       • 	 CSS na-azọpụta ọtụtụ ọrụ. Ọ nwere ike ijikwa okirikiri nke ibe weebụ n'otu oge 

       • 	 Echekwara akwa mpụga na faili CSS


       	 Gini kpatara iji CSS? 

       A na-eji CSS kọwaa ụdị maka ibe weebụ gị, gụnyere imewe, okirikiri na ọdịiche dị na ngosipụta maka ngwaọrụ dị iche na nha ihuenyo. 



       CSS doziri nnukwu nsogbu 

       Achọghị HTML dị ka ihe nwere mkpado maka ị mepụta ibe weebụ. 

       Emepụtara HTML iji kọwaa ihe dị na ibe weebụ, dị ka: 

       	 <h1>This is a heading</h1>

       	 <p>This is a paragraph.</p>



       	 Mgbe mkpado dịka <font>, ma tinye njiri mara agba na nkọwapụta HTML 3.2, ọ malitere nro maka ndị mmepe web. Mmepe nke weebụsaịtị weebụ buru ibu, ebe agbakwunyere mkpụrụ akwụkwọ na ozi agba na ibe ọ bụla, ghọrọ usoro dị ogologo ma dị ọnụ. 

       	 Iji dozie nsogbu a, World Wide Web Consortium (W3C) mepụtara CSS. 

       	 CSS wepụrụ usoro nhazi ụdị na ibe HTML! 

       	 CSS azọputara Lọt Ọrụ 

       	 A na-echekwa nkọwa n'ụzọ dabara adaba na faịlụ .css. 

       	 Site na faịlị uwe mpụga, ị nwere ike ịgbanwe ọdịdị nke weebụsaịtị du site n'ịgbanwe naanị otu faịlụ! 



       Nhazi CSS na ndi nhota 


       	 CSS Syntax 

       Ihe t-CSS setịpụrụ mebere onye na-ahọpụtara ihe na nkwupụta nkwupute: 



       	 Onye ahọpụtara na-arụtụ aka na HTML HTML ịchọrọ ịke. 

       	 Nkwupụta nkwupute ahụ nwere otu nkwupụta amamịghe nke mkpụrụedemede kewapụrụ. 

       Nkwupụta nke ọ bụla gụnyere aha ihe onwunwe CSS na ọnụ ahịa ya, ndị colon na-ekewa. 

       	 Nkwupụta CSS na-ejikarị eme mkpọtụ emechi mgbe nile, ihe nkwado na-agbagọkwa gburugburu. 

       N'ịma atụ na - esote, ihe niile <p> ga - adị n'etiti, na iji ederede uhie: 



       	 Ihe Nlereanya 

       	 p {

        	 color: red; 

        	 text-align: center; 

       	 } 



       Ndị na-ahọrọ CSS 

       A na-eji ndị na-ahọrọ CSS ka ha 'chọta' (ma ọ bụ họrọ) HTML ihe sitere na aha mmewere, id, klas, njirimara na ndị ọzọ. 



       Ihe ntinye ihe nlere 

       'The element selector ahọrọ ihe dabere na mmewere aha. 

       	 can nwere ike ịhọrọ ihe niile <p> na ibe dị ka nke a (na nke a, ihe niile <p> ga-ahaziri, yana otu ederede uhie): 



       	 Ihe Nlereanya 

       	 p {

       	  text-align: center; 

       	  color: red; 

       	 } 



       	 id Selector 


idọpụtara id na-eji njirimara id nke HTML maka ịhọrọ otu akọwapụtara. 

       	 The id nke mmewere kwesịrị ịbụ pụrụ iche n’ime ibe, yabụ ejiri onye na-ahọrọ id iji họrọ otu ihe pụrụ iche! 

       	 Ka ịhọrọ mmewere nwere otu ụdị ederede, dee agwa hash (#), na-esochi ụdị mmewere. 

       	 A ga-etinye ụkpụrụ ụdị dị n'okpuru ebe a na HTML maka id = "para1": 

       	 Ihe Nlereanya 

       	 #para1 {

        	 text-align: center; 

       	  color: red; 

       	 } 



       Onye klas Selector 

       'Klaasị na - ahọpụtara ihe klas nwere njiri mara otu 

       	 Ka ịhọrọ ndị nwere klas a kapịrị ọnụ, dee akara (.) agwa, aha klaasị sochiri ya. 

       	 N'ihe atụ dị n'okpuru ebe a, ihe HTML niile nwere klaasị = "etiti" ga-acha ọbara ma hazie: 


       	 Ihe Nlereanya 

       	.center {

       	  text-align: center; 

       	  color: red; 

       	 } 


       	 cannwekwara ike ịkọwapụta na ọ bụ naanị klas ga-emetụta HTML ụfọdụ. 

       	 Ihe atụ dị n'okpuru, naanị <p> ihe nwere klaasị = "etiti" ga - arụ ọrụ etiti: 


       	 Ihe Nlereanya \ n
       	 p.center {

       	  text-align: center; 

       	  color: red; 

       	 } 



       	 HTML ihe nwekwara ike zoo aka na otu klaasị. 

       \ t N'ihe atụ dị n'okpuru ebe a, ihe <p> ga-ahazi dịka klas = "etiti" yana klaasị = "buru ibu": 


       	 Ihe Nlereanya 

       	 <p class="center large">paragraf a na-ezo aka na klaasị abụọ. </p> 


       	 Mara: Aha klaasị enweghị ike imalite na ọnụọgụ! 



       	 Ndị Nhọrọ Ndị Nhọrọ

       	 O buru na inwere ihe dikwa otu ha di, otu a: 


       	 Ihe Nlereanya 


       	 h1 {

       	  text-align: center; 

       	  color: red; 

       	 }


       	 h2 {

       	  text-align: center; 

       	  color: red; 

       }


       	 p {

        	 text-align: center; 

       	  color: red; 

       	 } 



       	 Ọ ga-aka mma ịkpọkọta ndị ahọpụtara, iji belata koodu. 

       Banye otu na-ahọpụta ndị na-ahọrọ ha, kewapụ onye ọ bụla na-ahọpụta ya na komama. 

       N'ịma atụ dị n'okpuru, anyị chịkọtara ndị ahọpụtara site na koodu nke dị n'elu: 


       	 Ihe Nlereanya 

       	 h1, h2, p {

        	 text-align: center;

         	 color: red;

       	 }

               			OFdị ụdị ụlọ nbipụta 


       tzọ tozọ Atinye CSS 

       	Enwere ụzọ atọ eji etinye akwụkwọ mpempe akwụkwọ: 

       • 	Mpempe akwụkwọ mpụga 

       • 	Mpempị ụdị nke ime 

       • 	ụdị inline 



       Mpempe Styledị Mpụga 

       	Iji mpempe akwụkwọ mpụga, ị nwere ike ịgbanwe ọdịdị nke weebụsaịtị zuru oke site na 

       	na-agbanwe naanị otu faịlụ! 

       	ibe obula aghaghi itinye ntinye aka na mpempe uzo ozo nke di n\’ime <link> 
	element. Akụ <link> na-abanye n’ime ngalaba <head>: 


       	 Ihe Nlereanya 


       <head>

       <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="mystyle.css">
       </head> 



       	Enwere ike ide mpempe akwụkwọ mpụga na ndezi ederede ọ bụla. Faịlị ekwesịghị inwe mkpado any HTML. A ga-echekwa faịlị mpempe akwụkwọ na ndọtị .css. 

       	 Ihe Nlereanya 

       	body {

       	  background-color: lightblue; 

       	}


       	h1 {

        	 color: navy; 

        	 margin-left: 20px; 

       	} 



       	Mara: Etinyekwa oghere n’etiti ihe onwunwe na otu ya (dịka oke aka ekpe : 20 px;). Correctzọ ziri ezi bụ: oke-ekpe: 20px; 



       Mpempe Styledị N'ime Ahụ 

       	Enwere ike iji mpempe akwụkwọ odide ime ma ọ bụrụ na otu peeji nwere ụdị pụrụ iche. 

       A na-akọwa ụdị n'ime n'ime <style> element, n'ime ngalaba <head> nke ibe 	HTML: 


       	 Ihe Nlereanya 

       	<head>

       	<style>

       	body {

        	background-color: linen; 

       	}


       	h1 {

       	  color: maroon; 

        	 margin-left: 40px; 

       	} 

       	</style>

       	</head> 



       Ndepụta dị n'ime 

       Enwere ike iji ụdị inline tinye ụdị pụrụ iche maka otu mmewere. 

       	Iji jiri udiri inline mee ihe, gbakwunye njiri mara nke dabara adaba. \Dị 
\ tattribute nwere ike ịnwe ihe onwunwe CSS. 

       	Ihe atụ dị n'okpuru ebe a na-egosi otu esi agbanwe agba na akara aka ekpe nke <h1> 
\ telement: 


       	 Ihe Nlereanya 

       	 <h1 style="color:blue;margin-left:30px;">This is a heading</h1>

			Ederede CSS 

 Agba Text 
 	 A na-eji ihe eji agba idozi agba nke ederede. Akọwapụtara na agba ahụ: 
 • 	 aha agba - dị ka "uhie" 
 	 Ahịrị ederede maka ibe akọwapụtara na ahụ ahọpụtara. 

 	 nlere 
 	 body {
 	 color: blue; 
 	 }

	 h1 {
 	 color: green; 
 	 } 


Ederede itinye n'ọnọdụ 
 A na-eji ihe ederede-itinye n'ọnọdụ nke ederede iji dozie eriri kwụ ọtọ ederede. 
 	 ederede nwere ike aka ekpe ma ọ bụ aka nri, kwezie, ma ọ bụ zie ezi. 
 Ihe atụ a na-egosi na etinyere ederede n'etiti, na aka ekpe na aka nri ederede (aka ekpe 
 Ntinye ederede bụ ndabara ma ọ bụrụ na ntụzịaka aka ekpe-aka-nri, ma ka idozi ntinye aka nri bu oburu ma ọ bụrụ ederede 
 	 direction is right-to-left): 

 Nlele 
 	 h1 {
 	 text-align: center; 
 	 }

	 h2 {
 	 text-align: left; 
 	 }

Odikwa ederede 
 A na-eji ihe ịchọ mma ederede iji wepu ma ọ bụ wepu ihe ndozi ederede. 
 	 Ihe ndozi ederede bara uru: odighi; a na-ejikarị wepu gosipụta na njikọ: 
 	 Nlele 
 	 a {
 	 text-decoration: none; 
 	 } 
 	 The other text-decoration values are used to decorate text: 
 	 Nlele 
 	 h1 {
 	 text-decoration: overline; 
 	 }

	 h2 {
 	 text-decoration: line-through; 
 	 }


Ederede mgbanwe 
 	A na-eji ihe ederede-ederede iji kọwaa mkpụrụedemede ukwu na nke nta na ederede. 
 Enwere ike iji ya mee ihe niile ka ọ bụrụ obere mkpụrụedemede ukwu na nke pere mpe, ma ọ bụ jiri akara 
 	 leta mbu nke okwu obula: 

 Nlele 
 	 p.uppercase {
 	 text-transform: uppercase; 
 	 }

	 p.lowercase {
 	 text-transform: lowercase; 
 	 }


CSS Fonts 

Font ezinaulo 
 	 Ezi font nke ederede ya ka atọrọ ya na ihe ulo ezighi ezi ya. 
 Ngwongwo ulo font kwesiri inwe otutu font di ka "ida ada" usoro. Ọ bụrụ na 
 	 nchọgharị anaghị akwado font nke mbụ, ọ na-anwale font na-esote, na ndị ọzọ. 
 	 Bido na font ichoro, ma jiri ezinulo bipute mechie, ka ihe nchọgharị wee bulie 
 Ọ bụ font yiri ibe ya na ezinụlọ jikọtara ọnụ, ọ bụrụ na enweghị fotin ọzọ dị. 
 	 Mara: Ọ bụrụ na aha font ezinụlọ karịrị otu mkpụrụ okwu, ọ ga-abụrịrị na ntụte okwu, 	 ka: "Times New Roman". 
 A kọwara ihe karịrị otu ezinụlọ font na ndepụta nkewa: 

 Nlele 
 	 p {
 	 font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif; 
 	 } 


Font Style 
 A na-ejikarị ihe eji eme ihe iji dee ederede italic. 
 	 Ngwongwo a nwere ihe ato: 
 • 	 nkịtị - Egosiputa ederede dika odi 
 • \ Italic - E gosipụtara ederede n'ozi nkịtị 
