 The + Hakanan za'a iya amfani da afareta don ƙara (haɗakarwa) igiyoyi. 
 Misali 
 var txt1 = "Ahmed"; 
 var txt2 = "Mujahid"; 
 var txt3 = txt1 + "" + txt2; 
 Sakamakon txt3 zai kasance: 
 Ahmed Mujahid 
 The + = Hakanan za'a iya amfani da mai ba da sabis don ƙara (concatenate) kirtani: 
 Misali 
 var txt1 = "Sannu"; 
txt1 + = "Sir Musa"; 
 Sakamakon txt1 zai kasance: 
 Sannu Sir Musa 
 Lokacin da ake amfani da shi akan kirtani, ana kiran mai + afareta mai gudanarwa ta atomatik. 

	 dingara kirtani da Lambobi 
 Adara lambobi biyu, zai dawo da jimlar, amma ƙara lamba da igiya za su dawo da kirtani: 
 Misali 
 var x = 5 + 10; 
 var y = "5" + 5; 
 var z = "Yayi kyau" + 5; 
 Sakamakon x, y, da z zai kasance: 
 15 
55 
 Nagari5 
 Idan ka kara lamba da kirtani, sakamakon zai zama zaren! 

