 Lambobi biyu na iya zama masu karantu: 
 Misali 
 var x = 100 + 50; 
 ko masu canji: 
 Misali 
 var x = a + b; 
 ko maganganu: 
 Misali 
 var x = (100 + 50) * a; 

Ma'aikata da Ma'aikata 
 Lambobin (a cikin aikin ilimin lissafi) ana kiransu operands. 
 Mai sarrafawa ya bayyana aikin (da za'ayi a tsakanin ma'aikatan nan biyu) Operand Mai aiki Operand 
